{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A survival management simulator in which you must produce enough fuel to leave Mars before an incoming sandstorm destroys your base. Explore new places by collecting algae and bacteria to improve fuel production, but be careful because fuel is consumed as you travel! Upgrade your base's machinery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE GOAL IS TO LEAVE THE WILD MARS ...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">... but you need <strong>MORE AND MORE FUEL</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Produce fuel to return to Earth.  You'll find new elements that you can combine to improve fuel production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE CHALLENGE IS SURVIVING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage oxygen and energy, make water from ice, resist cold and radiation, grow food, mine minerals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Environments to upgrade with faster and most advanced technologies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Research and combine new elements to improve fuel production</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Upgrade your equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Survive into your base on the wild Mars!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727792063","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870620/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727792063","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870620/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727792063","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870620/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727792063","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_descrip